{"tid":1672118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警又虐畜","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T02:21:10.000Z","uid":296179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16f48ca9e1f2aa350e701b6a09d92d2b35c65a79","tid":1672118,"uid":296179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"有養狗都知，狗隻直立係違反自然，會為脊柱施予極大壓力。長久會引致癱瘓。特別係相中的大型犬隻。<br />\n呼籲大家寫去 SPAC 要求公開譴責。<br />\n<br />\n網址:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.spca.org.hk/ch/join-us/contact-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spca.org.hk%2Fch%2Fjoin-us%2Fcontact-us&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUofch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=3289a77a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.spca.org.hk/ch/join-us/contact-us</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nDear SPCA,<br />\n<br />\nThe HK Police posted a photo on their Facebook page today, showing their dog  was ordered to sit upright.<br />\n<br />\nThe propose of their post is to convince the public that their dogs are healthy even after working amidst teargas without proper protection. However this post in itself is harmful to the dog, as sitting upright would exert huge pressure on their spine, doing so for a prolonged period will even result in paralysis. <br />\n<br />\nI urge SPAC to condemn the Police publicly to for the precious well-being of the animals. Thank you !<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUPHryv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUPHryv.png&h=12f108d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYFzhFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYFzhFc.png&h=c7bd2d03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyvoa0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu